---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Inspect and manage friends of the active account

Usage: friends <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list    List friends of the active account
  add     Send or accept a friend request according to the current relationship
  remove  Remove a friend or cancel an outgoing friend request
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
